item.description: Alfred - TryHackme’s Room Writeup [Task 1] - Getting Initial Access For this room it seems we’ll need Nishang in order to gain access to the machine by using reverse shell scripts. So lets start by listing the links to get this Nishang tool: Nishang: Click here to access the repository and get this Powershell toolset. Alfred Room on THM: Click here to visit this room on TryHackme platform. Ok once you have that tool downloaded to your system we can get started.
